text: Jaime Blanco García (1 May 194424 September 2020) was a Spanish politician. He was President of Cantabria between 1990 and 1991. He was born in Santander, Cantabria. He was a member of the Spanish Socialist Workers' Party. Blanco García died on 24 September 2020, aged 76.Fallece el histórico socialista cántabro Jaime Blanco ==References== Category:1944 births Category:2020 deaths Category:Presidents of Cantabria
